Package: emacs24-bin-common
Architecture: any
Depends: emacs24-share-common (= ${source:Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
  gnutls-bin
Description: GNU Emacs editor's shared, architecture dependent files
 GNU Emacs is the extensible self-documenting text editor.
 This package contains the architecture dependent infrastructure
 that's shared by emacs24-x, emacs24-x-lucid, and emacs24-no-x.

